---
id: invite
---

%header
  .container
    %h1
      Invite

%section
  .container
    %p
      As a member of Uplink you receive three invites which let you bring more developers on board.
      %br
      Please invite the three most capable freelancer developers you know in Berlin!
      %br
      Simply fill out the form below and we will contact your invitee personally (no autogenerated mail) to see if she wants to join Uplink.

    = form_tag t(:form_url) do
      = hidden_field_tag '_subject', value: 'Invite'
      .form-group
        = label_tag 'email', caption: 'Your email'
        = email_field_tag 'email', id: 'email', class: 'form-control', required: true, placeholder: 'your@email.com'
      .form-group
        = label_tag 'invitee_email', caption: 'Invitee email'
        = email_field_tag 'invitee_email', id: 'invitee_email', class: 'form-control', required: true, placeholder: 'your-buddys@email.com'
      .form-group
        = label_tag 'invitee_name', caption: 'Invitee name'
        = text_field_tag 'invitee_name', id: 'invitee_name', class: 'form-control', required: true, placeholder: 'Tim Taylor'
      = submit_tag 'Submit', class: 'btn btn-lg btn-primary', data: { :'loading-text' => 'Please wait...' }
    .alert.alert-success
      Thanks! We'll contact your invitee shortly! If you want to invite someone else, please refresh the page.
    .alert.alert-danger
      Uh-oh! Something went wrong... please try again!
